reviewText: I find this to be very wholesome for my children. The story line is as interesting to the boys as the girls. My children watch this series over and over. Thank YOU!!!

reviewText: This is another section of the Saddle Club girls' lives on their school horse place. More life lessons are learned about horses and friendships that are deeply tested at times too. The main girls are now 13.

reviewText: I bought this for my horse loving daughter, she loves it! Deals with both the girls' emotions, real life things girls deal with and horses.
